net.cloud.server.util

Class HashObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.server.util.HashObj
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bufferable

    public final class HashObj
extends Object
implements Bufferable
    A lack of creativity with the name... An object which stores the results of the hash function on some data. Only the hash is kept, not the original data.
    This object is immutable.
